notification.template.user_business_expi: We cordially remind you that the service for your Milesight account in the {1}{2}{3} will expire on {4}{5}{6}. To ensure the continuity of your service benefits and related resources, we recommend that you promptly reach out to Milesight so that we can assist you with account renewal or any other requirements you may have.
Important Reminder: Your Service Has Expired

In case you are unable to complete the renewal before this date, we understand and offer you a 15-day grace period. During this period, your account privileges will remain unchanged, and all added devices, created applications, and related services will continue to function normally. However, please note that if you have purchased a service resource that allows for uploading pictures, the pictures reported by your devices during this time will still count towards the resource usage.

However, should the expiration issue remain unresolved after the grace period ends, we will be compelled to make necessary adjustments to your account according to our service terms. Specifically, we will disable and restrict access to services and resources that exceed our free service standards. This includes, but is not limited to, newly created applications (including their API and Webhook functionalities) and devices, which will no longer be accessible. Additionally, it is crucial to remind you that any unsaved data during the period of service restrictions may not be recoverable, potentially causing inconvenience to your business. Furthermore, if you choose to renew your account more than 15 days after your devices have been disabled, due to technical reasons, the restoration of these devices from the disabled state may take longer than a day, depending on actual circumstances. Therefore, we urge you to take this seriously and prepare in advance to avoid potential risks.
Regarding our free service standards, we reaffirm the following:

Please plan your resource usage accordingly based on the above standards and contact us promptly to handle your account renewal. The Milesight team remains committed to providing you with high-quality and efficient services, and we look forward to collaborating with you for an even brighter future.

Should you have any questions or require assistance, please do not hesitate to reach out to us via our customer service hotline or official email. We wish you a pleasant life and successful endeavors!
